97e20b65e53f45a81","tid":774392,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T15:34:07.000Z","msg":"係資產負債表上面俾你見到行&rdquo;應付未付&rdquo;咪姐係入咗賬。。。"}]}